      },
      "level": {
        "value": 16
      },
      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role (A94 / A67 / A45):</strong> the <strong>horned devil</strong> warding the castle's towers and air — roosting atop Seawatch Tower (A94), patrolling invisibly (20% chance per balcony transit he spots non-stealthy PCs), winding the Epochal clock monthly, and ambushing the main-stair approach from A67. He serves Ileosa to repay an ancient debt to @UUID[Compendium.cotct-pf2e-conversion.cotct-actors.Actor.sermignattoDvl01]{Sermignatto}; a 'Needlehearted' pain-philosopher and patron of Ustalav's Black Horn cult. His gear — Flesh Shredder and the ring — is the A94 treasure.</p>",
